{"tid":221101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特朗普警告】或最終同北韓爆大衝突 ! !","createTime":"2017-04-28T12:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T01:43:57.000Z","uid":28366,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d79f355532028a423a87a154f5c5ee960dfd91b","tid":221101,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"朝鮮半島局勢持續升溫，美國總統特朗普周四直言他最大的全球憂慮就是北韓，稱美國與北韓有機會發生「重大、重大」的軍事衝突，呼籲美國不要輕視這個可能性。<br />\n<br />\n外界相信北韓即將進行試射或第6次核試，特朗普表示：「我們絕對有機會最終要與北韓爆發一次重大、重大的衝突。」他希望可以避免一戰，同時以和平方法與平壤達成無核化協議，但強調：「我們想用外交方式解決問題，但實在非常困難。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普雖然在北韓問題上多次批評中國國家主席習近平，但他態度見軟化，指相信對方「盡一切所能努力嘗試」化解危機，「他肯定不想見到亂局及傷亡，我知道他都想有能力做點事，但或者他無能為力」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普亦未有輕視年紀輕輕就接位的領袖金正恩，「不是有很多27歲男人可以上台接管一個政權」。美國本周加速在南韓部署「戰區高空防禦系統」（THAAD，下稱「薩德」），特朗普貫徹選前要求盟友分擔軍費的要求，稱他希望南韓支付10億美元（78億港元）的費用。但南韓國防部今早回應指，無意改變現行由美國負責經費的做法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170428/56624352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170428%2F56624352&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZogRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c3c991cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170428%2F56624352&h=375d2abf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170428/56624352</a>"},{"pid":"0d7e86d96e280bcdcf06d4c0b59851e402599eec","tid":221101,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:44:46.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"7a5135151a61c41609f9876670c1e39200bdae6b","tid":221101,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗯</blockquote><br />\n預左架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7bb99af357bc8afa98b387cc712f2de52ef6a2","tid":221101,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嗯</blockquote><br />\n預左架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n預左架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa30d35038030b9594e4eccb8bd00060ca72a97","tid":221101,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"唔係話叫習大大擺平金仔單野咩？"},{"pid":"ec4879a539400f87edd3a36ce0c3e3873540e34a","tid":221101,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:52:54.000Z","msg":"南韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc08ba3b552a68908ead46a9adbaf7fce30955dd","tid":221101,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:53:04.000Z","msg":"講左成個月啦喎 係就快"},{"pid":"c64dbb97212fac1ddff13fecb85d57f582ebf318","tid":221101,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:00:35.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"149317cf43da1fc242216cce5f456a42b26eaeaf","tid":221101,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"538eead7dff3f65339b3b06e006d6e8de0fbb77c","tid":221101,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068474609031d05d6d4bb7d6b26ee7753c83ea14","tid":221101,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講左成個月啦喎 係就快</blockquote><br />\n金仔唔核試玩條毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75eb31a7b5919222c9e2fdfa9507037f5252705","tid":221101,"uid":14080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:05:40.000Z","msg":"Zzz"},{"pid":"99b614de8698162320fcce3567a9a33d17afada7","tid":221101,"uid":40318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n特朗普亦未有輕視年紀輕輕就接位的領袖金正恩，「不是有很多27歲男人可以上台接管一個政權」。美國本周加速在南韓部署「戰區高空防禦系統」（THAAD，<span style=\"color: red;\">下稱「薩德」</span>），特朗普貫徹選前要求盟友分擔軍費的要求，稱他希望南韓支付10億美元（78億港元）的費用。但南韓國防部今早回應指，無意改變現行由美國負責經費的做法。<br />\n]</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇到r哂頭"},{"pid":"0fc5aae626cc04093eeca0cf1ec8a8ed426b183a","tid":221101,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:16:09.000Z","msg":"seen"},{"pid":"f8a8a71a8c2422a706de9d9962e746760b2bbfc0","tid":221101,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:16:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25aa72c53fdb38bac60d7e05fb728516d8d08367","tid":221101,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我知道他都想有能力做點事，但或者他無能為力」。</span><br />\n即係話鳩棋王係廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d15f42509f2b98c6d6b213b08a8aba31f22ae0","tid":221101,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"英文叫major conflict<br />\n聽落又好似唔係好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc75333bb8ba81c2dc52070020f78ae94881db0","tid":221101,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"4/15<br />\n美國：好大機會同北韓爆大衝突<br />\n北韓：試射下幾枝炮彈當試左<br />\n<br />\n4/20<br />\n美國：好大機會同北韓爆大衝突<br />\n北韓：試射下幾枝炮彈當試左<br />\n<br />\n4/25<br />\n美國：好大機會同北韓爆大衝突<br />\n北韓：試射下幾枝炮彈當試左<br />\n<br />\n4/30<br />\n美國：好大機會同北韓爆大衝突<br />\n北韓：試射下幾枝炮彈當試左<br />\n<br />\n...."},{"pid":"bd22687bc609f89b7fc11a992c6b67a54c38c28a","tid":221101,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>雲佩斯警告：曼聯下季皇者回歸<br />\n<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n雲佩斯對其他英超對手發起警告......<br />\n<br />\n曼聯這個賽季令人失望，在莫耶斯帶領下已鐵定無緣下季歐聯賽事，而這位費格遜接班人亦在千夫所指下被紅魔解僱。曼聯於上場比賽在主場大勝侯城3-1，射手雲佩斯賽後接受官方電視訪問時自信滿滿，表示紅魔將在下個賽季強勢回歸。<br />\n<br />\n「相信我，球隊將會在下個賽季捲土重來！不信的話，你大可以紀錄低這句說話。」<br />\n<br />\n以球員身份暫代領隊一職的傑斯，除了在最後20分鍾以球員身份上場外，亦在賽後的告別演講中，呼籲球迷繼續支持曼聯。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZogRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ffb83a62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"9f31f5ea7762707947a92d81f82e9ba12b634829","tid":221101,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好大盤棋<br />\n侵侵vs習棋王"},{"pid":"f97596433773d9843893953be2e20c67d769ee25","tid":221101,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4/15<br />\n美國：好大機會同北韓爆大衝突<br />\n北韓：試射下幾枝炮彈當試左<br />\n<br />\n4/20<br />\n美國：好大機會同北韓爆大衝突<br />\n北韓：試射下幾枝炮彈當試左<br />\n<br />\n4/25<br />\n美國：好大機會同北韓爆大衝突<br />\n北韓：試射下幾枝炮彈當試左<br />\n<br />\n4/30<br />\n美國：好大機會同北韓爆大衝突<br />\n北韓：試射下幾枝炮彈當試左<br />\n<br />\n....</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef96bb025ed7ac41f0e0ad61337cea97de803e1d","tid":221101,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:59:59.000Z","msg":"連股票市場都對呢件事無撚哂反應 有d低賤連登仔仲日日諗住打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec8eae3b61b160fb324643f663c7c16b6dc5d7b","tid":221101,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}